  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I think that was the most horrible night of my life, like a Chinese torture.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I know it was blood, because I felt it was like glue sticking to me.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And one more horrible experience was that every morning there-- we did not do a thing.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And [INAUDIBLE] was the [INAUDIBLE] appell.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That is when they chase everybody out to a huge area, and they count numbers.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was very advisable to get out as soon as one can from the barrack, because the last few dozen were kept behind, and they were dragging out the dead ones to the mass grave.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And not only it was hard work to schlep them, to carry them to the grave and throw them in, but those playful SS, when they were in the mood, they kicked those in too who were throwing, and then-- so everybody tried to run out as fast as they can, could.",
      "word_count": 52
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And one morning I was running out as fast as I could, and a guy a few steps ahead of me fell-- fell into a little puddle of water, and was actually drowning in maybe five inches of water.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And for that second, should I stop and try to help him?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because I thought I knew him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was one of my original guys that I was together with.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Or should I just take care of myself?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I did not stop.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And because of it, for many, many years, I had nightmares seeing that scene, that that guy is drowning, you know, making gargling, in-- in that little water.",
      "word_count": 28
    }
  ],
